text: RKS Teanoai II (301) at Austal shipyards in Henderson, Western Australia, in April 2020. RKS Teanoai II (301) will be the eighth built by Australian shipbuilding firm Austal for Australia's Pacific Islands Forum neighbours. She was launched on April 24, 2020, and is scheduled to be delivered to the Kiribati Police later in 2020. She will replace the 35 year old Pacific Forum patrol vessel also named . ==References== Category:2020 ships Category:Guardian class patrol vessels Category:Naval ships of the Kiribati
